{"tid":720361,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[最強的劍與盾]傳暗撻3個月 江嘉敏出招冧掂余德丞","createTime":"2018-06-28T00:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T10:42:18.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"63fcd0120565392f52e38eebff2a7565cab42c00","tid":720361,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:58:12.000Z","msg":"入行只有3年的無綫力捧小花江嘉敏，每齣劇都會與合作的小生傳出緋聞，異性緣極強。新一期《東周刊》報道，江嘉敏因拍新劇《危城First Lady》，與超級「筍盤」余德丞戲假情真，並已暗撻3個月。<br />\n<br />\n　　身為前香港游泳代表隊成員的余德丞是「巨胸小鮮肉」，跟父母一家三口居於跑馬地大坑道嘉園，一個市值近2千萬的豪宅單位，再加上家人手持的其他物業，總市值逾半億元。<br />\n<br />\n　　據片場工作人員透露，江嘉敏不時請零食及送上靚湯冧掂余德丞，男方則日日做「柴可夫」管接送，甜蜜滿瀉。二人在劇中有感情線，奉旨談情，更不避嫌在社交平台上載「蜜照」，兼公開打情罵俏。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/085241_cd3b773bf0c2e16ef9c3a11183d4617e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F085241_cd3b773bf0c2e16ef9c3a11183d4617e.jpg&h=627f2dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/2_14526559205abca5b574319-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F2_14526559205abca5b574319-800x450.jpg&h=7cc57e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.showwall.com/wp/dickson_yu/free/332418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.showwall.com%2Fwp%2Fdickson_yu%2Ffree%2F332418.jpg&h=5e014cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次真係好有火花"},{"pid":"c60269ba6a056bd5305a608ff90a40eb94d76b5d","tid":720361,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T01:03:55.000Z","msg":"肛交吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個名都淫過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a96dc88f34b7699222403e46fc02c8eb59de0f5","tid":720361,"uid":93783,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T01:10:23.000Z","msg":"佢好慘 成日被人老屈鍾